#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.41:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: cūlavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "an3.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Cūḷavagga"
msgstr "5. The Lesser Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Sammukhībhāvasutta"
msgstr "41. Present"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.41:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tiṇṇaṃ, bhikkhave, sammukhībhāvā saddho kulaputto bahuṃ puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when three things are present, a faithful person from a good "
"family makes much merit."

msgctxt "an3.41:1.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.41:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhāya, bhikkhave, sammukhībhāvā saddho kulaputto bahuṃ puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr "When faith is present,"

msgctxt "an3.41:1.4"
msgid ""
"Deyyadhammassa, bhikkhave, sammukhībhāvā saddho kulaputto bahuṃ puññaṃ "
"pasavati."
msgstr "when a gift to give is present,"

msgctxt "an3.41:1.5"
msgid ""
"Dakkhiṇeyyānaṃ, bhikkhave, sammukhībhāvā saddho kulaputto bahuṃ puññaṃ "
"pasavati."
msgstr "and when those worthy of a teacher’s offering are present."

msgctxt "an3.41:1.6"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ sammukhībhāvā saddho kulaputto bahuṃ puññaṃ "
"pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When these three things are present, a faithful person from a good family "
"makes much merit.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.41:1.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
